{"tid":1144623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔公平］點解c朗拿度靠一場波就可以反cap美斯風向","createTime":"2019-05-08T07:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T02:45:52.000Z","uid":43785,"like":19,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"16dc21a2773d2fe504d452612077e99e172e76e0","tid":1144623,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibZgd5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibZgd5z.png&h=4a9e3ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aTwNqA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aTwNqA.gif&h=2e27760a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實美斯已經好努力，可惜比利物浦防守阻住，難砌得好犀利。<br />\n前面入左三球，明明今次輸波係因為後防做得差， 同美斯冇乜關係。<br />\n再好嘅球員，冇好嘅隊友，又點會贏波。<br />\n點解又可以將失敗怪落美斯度。<br />\n美斯入幾多球都冇用啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GByXHZU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGByXHZU.gif&h=c980ba5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5x9WYx9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5x9WYx9.gif&h=bf13f08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相反C朗拿度對阿積士，進攻位都做唔好，淨係識得j眼神，屌隊友做得差，嫌鳩人老，唔肯跑。<br />\n做埋啲對場波冇用嘅嘢。 <br />\n淨係識得賴地硬，根本帶唔起成隊波。<br />\n<br />\n憑乜嘢親美斯輸波，就想反CAP風向。<br />\n我覺得好唔公平。"},{"pid":"496b7f7c0e6b8a79a7c6fee609154ddf5e34c5a6","tid":1144623,"uid":102480,"like":28,"dislike":54,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"c朗屌鳩隊友=激勵隊友<br />\nc朗發哂脾氣=c朗爭勝心好強<br />\nc朗插水=好有計謀<br />\nc朗入唔到4強=隊友拖累<br />\n祖記拎到不嬲都拎到既意甲=c朗帶挈"},{"pid":"80a685a498d44cebaf38b318ec11424b0ccfc5c1","tid":1144623,"uid":9931,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"班疤迷比庇護工場cut左上網 <br />\n<br />\n所以有集體潛水呢個假象出現"},{"pid":"d74ae02b807a9032ff41da8d70c2c407d7d2e1dd","tid":1144623,"uid":36134,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"496b7f7c0e6b8a79a7c6fee609154ddf5e34c5a6","tid":1144623,"uid":102480,"l